# DEEPSEARCH ARSENAL | ZERO TRUST ARCHITECTURE (v8.1)

> **"Trust No One. Verify Everything."**

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Operational-green) ![Platform](https://img.shields.io/badge/Platform-Windows_PowerShell-blue) ![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Version-v8.1_Enterprise-cyan)

**DeepSearch Arsenal** is a military-grade cybersecurity framework designed for Windows environments. Unlike standard script collections, it operates on a **Zero Trust Kernel Architecture**, forcing strict verification for every process. It combines Offensive Red Team capabilities, Defensive Blue Team hardening, and advanced OSINT reconnaissance into a single, modular Hypervisor.

---

## âš¡ Key Features

* **Kernel Hypervisor (v8.1):** A central command center that manages all subsystems with error handling and crash protection.
* **Modular Architecture:** Tools are isolated into 5 operational divisions (OSINT, DEFENSE, OFFENSE, NET_OPS, MAINTENANCE).
* **Zero Trust Vault:** Critical data is encrypted using **AES-256** standards.
* **Watchdog Protocol:** Background monitoring system that ensures the Kernel remains active and uncompromised.
* **Stealth Mode:** Tools operate largely in memory to minimize forensic footprint.

